{"tid":111171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[今日新聞]  蝻亞漢涉暴力毆打打劫　鳳姐：佢係我撞到最衰嘅客","createTime":"2017-02-07T08:31:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T02:42:29.000Z","uid":23479,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"25258abf21b3c71443fffab1a037c007c18abd5b","tid":111171,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:31:10.000Z","msg":"02月07日(二) 12:43<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>持香港身份證</strong></span></span>、<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>能操廣東話的蝻亞裔男子</strong></span></span>，去年到深水埗光顧「一樓一鳳」惟之後指無錢付肉金，以出外提款為由，誘鳳姐到一後巷後，再<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>涉嫌拳毆她的頭至流血，再涉嫌偷去對方身上的1000港元後逃去</strong></span>。被告陳華勝昨承認一項傷人罪，但<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>否認</strong></span>一項盜竊罪。案件今於區院續審，事主X續作供，稱因安全理由，故她當時把放在櫃內的現金、電話及鎖匙帶走，一同隨被告往提款。<br />\n<br />\n辯方則指出被告身上有200港元，本打算先給部分款項，但X要求全數支付。X即指「No」，強調被告「一個仙都無」，指被告把褲袋等也倒出來讓她看過，被告身上沒有錢。X又指「佢係我撞到最衰嘅一個客人，所以印象非常之深刻」。<br />\n<br />\nX續稱被告往櫃員機提款時，聲稱櫃員機沒錢或是壞機等推塘，她卻看見別人都能成功提款，便懷疑「原來所有嘢係扮出黎嘅」。當兩人進入後巷前，X稱以手機偷拍被告相片，惟辯方卻質疑被告是自願被拍照，X遂解釋指「因為我電話有郁動的功能，所以有正面」。<br />\n<br />\n辯方又質疑X既然起疑，何以再隨被告入後巷，X即指「700蚊喎，我欠你700蚊，你都唔捨得啦，咪姑且一試」，心想被告的朋友可能真的在前面，「我唔知佢打我，佢打我嘅，我唔要喇」。X指事後額頭縫了4針，現仍有疤痕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170207/photo/bkn-20170207124353664-0207_00822_001_01b.jpg?20170207130709\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170207%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170207124353664-0207_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20170207130709&h=5efad3a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"559c34fec0af1c583f877588d94879ac335e48f3","tid":111171,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14debabed5403b3e39ee062ef45e44029c98964f","tid":111171,"uid":62494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:42:42.000Z","msg":"冇錢比都叫客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"d0f99c1e89f8da38092c3299ffde7b98b833e485","tid":111171,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:45:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ccb8bce178c60f78007e66a8f6710ce14a37b0a0","tid":111171,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:45:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b3fff03030e1181bdd0b9faa9a2bd62f38b8b67","tid":111171,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:46:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b450fe5a1b1e799458b0a9639b7d1b184e57b50","tid":111171,"uid":25945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T09:20:34.000Z","msg":"連企街都唔敢做蝻生意<br />\n呢位姐仔真勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3988c0bae1e269bb352c9d21095c7d4ec23a5c8","tid":111171,"uid":6702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T09:23:12.000Z","msg":"大愛撚呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n左膠呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nust蝻呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n進擊蝻呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fcee6a00b9e3036f333e2a60af3197709976fc4","tid":111171,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T09:26:23.000Z","msg":"雞錢都呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"163f7a104ffb4d95723eb485ba50026487cf458e","tid":111171,"uid":26279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T09:26:41.000Z","msg":"Ust南亞仔係邊"},{"pid":"1c600f6bed8bf64f3b67651fb3059caab2cefcd7","tid":111171,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T09:28:44.000Z","msg":"蝻叫雞要比錢就是歧視"},{"pid":"f6150dc940d5141a580bf2fd129679267fb939e7","tid":111171,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci